title: 11/26/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 11/26/21 DPS Best Of
description:
Jason McIntyre and Rob Parker, in for Dan, preview the matchup between the Rams and Packers this Sunday and debate Matt Stafford's performance since coming to Los Angeles. Jason explains why he believes the Warriors are the best team in the NBA right now. Ex-NFL Team Doctor Dr. David Chao joins the guys to discuss the biggest injury issues in the NFL right now, including Aaron Rodgers, Justin Fields, Ezekiel Elliott, and an update on Tre'Davious White. The guys react to another loss for the Cowboys and Rob breaks down why he thinks the Cowboys are frauds.
